with lieux as 
    (select l.*, icf."the_geom" as geom from "public"."lieux_prep_rn_with_city_code" l, "public"."ign_commune_france" icf where l."current_city_code" = icf."INSEE_COM"),
bornes as 
    (select b.*, icf."the_geom" as geom from "public"."bornes_routes_borne_suivante_2016" b, "public"."ign_commune_france" icf where b."INSEE_COM" = icf."INSEE_COM")
SELECT * 
FROM lieux l
LEFT JOIN bornes b
ON 
    (l.catr = 'autoroute' OR l.catr = "route nationale") 
    AND l."voie_normalise" = b."nom_courant_route" 
    AND l.pr = b.pr 
    AND ST_DWithin(l.geom::geography, b.geom::geography, 2000)

p665bdgl7n.sql:
with lieux as 
    (select l.*, icf."the_geom" as geom from "public"."lieux_prep_rn_with_city_code" l, "public"."ign_commune_france" icf where l."current_city_code" = icf."INSEE_COM"),
bornes as 
    (select b.*, icf."the_geom" as geom from "public"."bornes_routes_borne_suivante_2016" b, "public"."ign_commune_france" icf where b."INSEE_COM" = icf."INSEE_COM")
SELECT DISTINCT ON (l."Num_Acc") l.*, b.lat, b.lon, b.lat_next, b.lon_next, b."INSEE_COM" as pr_insee_com, b."NOM_COM" as pr_nom_com 
FROM lieux l
LEFT JOIN bornes b
ON 
    (l.catr = 'autoroute' OR l.catr = 'route nationale') 
    AND l."voie_normalise" = b."nom_courant_route" 
    AND l.pr = b.pr 
    AND ST_DWithin(l.geom::geography, b.geom::geography, 2000)
order by l."Num_Acc", ST_distance(l.geom, b.geom)
limit 100

With accidents as (select * from "public"."caracteristiques_coordinates_selected" where "Num_Acc" = '201500046804'),
SELECT "INSEE_COM", num_route_or_id, num_route_com_id, st_distance(st_point(accidents.longitude, accidents.latitude), the_geom) AS distance, geojson
     FROM "osm_routes_par_commune_geojson"  AS routes
     WHERE
        st_dwithin(routes.the_geom, st_point(longitude, latitude), 500)
        AND (
            (accidents.catr = 'autoroute' AND routes.cat_route_osm = 'autoroute')
            OR (accidents.catr = 'route nationale' AND routes.cat_route_osm = 'route principale')
            OR (accidents.catr != 'autoroute' AND accidents.catr != 'route nationale'))
     ORDER BY distance
    LIMIT 1

SELECT "INSEE_COM", num_route_or_id, num_route_com_id, st_distance(st_point(accidents.longitude, accidents.latitude), the_geom) AS distance, geojson
     FROM "osm_routes_par_commune_geojson"  AS routes, accidents
     WHERE
        st_dwithin(routes.the_geom, st_point(longitude, latitude), 500)
        AND (
            (accidents.catr = 'autoroute' AND routes.cat_route_osm = 'autoroute')
            OR (accidents.catr = 'route nationale' AND routes.cat_route_osm = 'route principale')
            OR (accidents.catr != 'autoroute' AND accidents.catr != 'route nationale'))
     ORDER BY distance
    LIMIT 1
